messages.content: //aight, I'mma post my stuff here both for lore and rules
//This one is for an experimental ruleset I've been working on called the "Do or Die" system
//I noticed in most RPs we have or Tabletops playthrough I see on Youtube, they tend to be really long as hell
//plus in tabletop it's overly complicated, you need shit like figurines and most DMs are rather strict with story
//So I made a simplified ruleset inspired by GURPS (well atleast the ruleset from Fallout's SPECIAL which is inspired by GURPS)
//It's actually kinda complete but there are some things that I had to adjust
//Like I originally made an attribute list like Fallout's SPECIAL but then I realized that I hardly use the Attributes, so I simplified to just having "health, actions within a turn and armor"
//I am currently making a mini campaign for this specific ruleset but like GURPS, the Do or Die system can be compatible with any genre
//Oh and this Ruleset can just be played between two people or more. Specifically the "Player Protagonist" and the Game Master or the "Game Antagonist"
//and if competitive, there can be score between the two
//So when I feel I wanna try something out, I'mma invite one of you guys
//also I'm just tired of not having my actions matter that much in RPing

//updated rules + Survival mod is finished (Choose your own adventure is optional)
https://drive.google.com/file/d/11cQp70w8OxXJgd7kueXJJYjdJBsHJlcT/view?usp=sharing

messages.content: *a tabletop floats out of the darkness in front of Actonsic*
*upon its wooden surface (it has no table legs) is the document accessible via the link*
*he picks it up and skims over it*
Looks like some kind of...Dungeons and Dragons simplified version.
Wonder why they'd make a whole channel for all this.
Yeah. What we were calling "rooms" and shit before.
It says I can assign 2 points to any skill, but doesn't list skills.
I'm assuming I can just make shit up.
Ha, ha. Very funny and cool of you, Giratina.
What does it mean to have +2 coolness?
I think the word you're supposed to use is, like...charisma.
But you don't know that word, do you?
Well it sounds like a cool word.
*sways head like a motion one would make when swishing their hair*
*hard to tell when he's got all those head-accessories*
*...trying to come up with an answer*
*kicks the table away, and it takes the document into the darkness*
Yeah, well, this place is still empty. Wanna keep moving?
//Right, I guess I can speak to the puppeteer.
(If you really want a Latias to come with you, why don't you make your own Latias?)
//I meant that I should've gone with her as my alibi instead of Ho-Oh. But I'll.

(Would've been even less believable
Oh, okay. I'll forget about it.)

messages.content: Hey, what the hell is all this?

Look! Did you bring Ho-Oh into existence just so she could back you up?
*also looks at the big gray box*
(I would totally have done that too)
Must be some kinda. Temporal anomaly.
That doesn't even make any sense.
Whatever. Are we going or what?
The hell are you doing G
Oh, they already found out about us.
What I'm doing is opening another rift, care to join?
*though the abomination is abominable, he is still sad to see Giratina turning down who Actonsic believes to be his only admirer*
//Damn, that's crazy. I can see what he's thinking.
(Don't you think you should say something? About that?)
